        <ontology:hasDescription>The average per capita income (EUR/year) [Province] is 3877. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Province] is 3286. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 4.99%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 27.78%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 67.22%. The per capita income (EUR/year) [Region] is 14578. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Region] is 12355. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 4.78%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 38.97%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 56.24%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
